1
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:34,519
Young Master

2
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:14,879
Brother

3
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,840
It's tough out here

4
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:17,960
Brother

5
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,719
We're all family here

6
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,199
Here

7
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:22,840
Take it

8
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,479
Take it

9
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:24,599
Don't be shy

10
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:34,599
It's fine, it's fine

11
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:35,960
This isn't my body anyway

12
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,080
I'm not embarrassed

13
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,759
It's the others
who'll be embarrassed.

14
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,120
Fourth Young Master

15
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,479
I bought these clothes for you

16
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:46,639
Please make do with them for now

17
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,159
Fourth Young Master

18
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,039
Your righteousness, brother,

19
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,360
I shall never forget

20
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,400
Until we meet again

21
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:33,680
Young Master

22
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,319
Why put yourself through all this?

23
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:36,879
You're a young master of Ning Manor

24
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,120
Just wait until you're of marrying age

25
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,840
Then you can get some silver from the manor

26
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,199
And live a comfortable life

27
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:43,439
Forget it

28
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,280
Give us one

29
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,240
Give us one

30
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:50,840
The Imperial Examination just ended today

31
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:53,080
Scholars are gathering at Top Scholar Pavilion

32
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,199
To recite poems and compose couplets

33
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,560
And if you stand out from the rest

34
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,360
You can win a thousand taels of silver

35
00:03:58,319 --> 00:03:59,159
A thousand taels of silver?

36
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,120
There's such a sweet deal?

37
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,000
Then I'd better hurry over

38
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:06,479
Writing poems for a thousand taels of silver?

39
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:09,960
Then I'd be unstoppable!

40
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,039
Young Master,
there's something you don't know

41
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:15,520
If among these poets

42
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:16,600
Someone actually becomes the Number One Scholar

43
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,839
That'd be Top Scholar Pavilion's
golden reputation

44
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:21,720
What a pity

45
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,040
Young Master, you are in Ning Manor

46
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,959
The Madam plays favorites
and won't let you study

47
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:27,279
Otherwise, in two years you could take
the Imperial Examination

48
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,160
And once you make the list

49
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,720
The Master would surely see you in a new light

50
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:30,800
By then

51
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:32,319
You'd be Your Excellency yourself

52
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,360
I couldn't care less

53
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:35,839
Where'd this old drunk come from?

54
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,120
Daring to dine and dash at our place!

55
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,480
Folks!

56
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:42,480
The workers at this tavern

57
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,399
Not only do they beat up an old man

58
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,759
They also sell fake wine!

59
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,000
Talk nonsense one more time

60
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:48,800
And I'll kick you to death

61
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:49,360
You!

62
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,399
Beggar, go beg somewhere else

63
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,519
Bullying an old man in broad daylight

64
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,959
Have you two no shame?

65
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,560
He dined and dashed

66
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,600
Is that supposed to be honorable?

67
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,600
You're standing up for him?

68
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:03,120
Then you pay up!

69
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,160
Fine, I'll pay

70
00:05:18,959 --> 00:05:19,600
Pay up!

71
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,000
Hurry up!

72
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,000
I...

73
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,480
Next time...

74
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:29,800
What do you mean, next time?

75
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,199
I'll beat you too!

76
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,040
Why are you hitting people?

77
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,759
Help! Is anyone there?

78
00:05:35,079 --> 00:05:35,879
I'm reporting this to the authorities!

79
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,000
Somebody, help!

80
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:38,240
They're beating someone in the street!

81
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:39,720
Get lost!

82
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:41,319
Don't ever come to our shop again!

83
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,079
Now scram!

84
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,319
Unbelievable.

85
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,439
Young Master.

86
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,680
Young Master.

87
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,399
Why put yourself through this?

88
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:49,480
Sir.

89
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,120
You saw that, didn't you?

90
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,600
These guys hit with no mercy.

91
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,480
Don't pull stunts like this anymore.

92
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,199
Xiao Mei, let's go.

93
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:56,920
Wait, no...

94
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,480
Oh, my dear son!

95
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:00,680
You can't abandon your father!

96
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,199
Sir, you're drunk.

97
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,160
Who's your son?

98
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,560
How could I be your son? Folks!

99
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,959
You be the judge here!

100
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:08,120
I struggled to raise him.

101
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,160
Now that I'm old,

102
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,759
he wants to abandon me.

103
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,759
You're trying to scam me!

104
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:14,279
Let go!

105
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,000
Young man,

106
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,439
you're in the wrong here.

107
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,399
No matter what a father does wrong,

108
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
he's still your father.

109
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,040
The laws of our dynasty state

110
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,240
that those who shun their elders

111
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,920
will face banishment to military service.

112
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:25,720
That's right.

113
00:06:25,839 --> 00:06:27,079
You'll face banishment
to military service.

114
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,439
This...

115
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,360
Young Master,

116
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,519
what do we do?

117
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:34,399
What else can we do?

118
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:36,839
How about...

119
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,079
we take him to your home too.

120
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,399
Slow down, slow down.

121
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,319
Auntie!

122
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,319
Auntie!

123
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:53,519
Mei Shi!

124
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,399
Let Auntie have a look at you.

125
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,360
Did you miss Auntie?

126
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,279
Yes!

127
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,199
Brother.

128
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,120
Sister-in-law.

129
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,120
Sis.

130
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:03,079
I was just talking about you
with your sister-in-law.

131
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,360
Little sister.

132
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,360
So, who are these two?

133
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,240
This is the Fourth Young Master
of Ning Manor.

134
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:09,920
Ning Chen.

135
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,560
And this elderly gentleman is...

136
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:14,240
So you're the one

137
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,120
the Fourth Young Master
my sister always mentions.

138
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,399
Sorry to intrude.

139
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,279
This elderly gentleman

140
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,360
is someone I happened to meet on the road.

141
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,279
Once he sobers up,

142
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,360
I'll deal with him.

143
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,639
Sister-in-law, brother.

144
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:29,240
I need to discuss something with you.

145
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,759
From now on,

146
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,160
I may not be working
at Ning Manor anymore.

147
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,959
The Fourth Young Master

148
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,000
will also be staying with us for a while.

149
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,759
Little sister,

150
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:44,800
you know our family's situation.

151
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,879
Your nephew will start school soon,

152
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:48,720
and we really need money right now.

153
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:49,959
If you've lost your job,

154
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,360
your brother and I supporting you

155
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,839
is only right and proper.

156
00:07:53,399 --> 00:07:53,959
But

157
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,399
if there's another mouth to feed,

158
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,279
how are we going to manage?

159
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:58,920
Watch your mouth.

160
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,720
Master Ning,

161
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,759
my wife doesn't know
how to speak properly.

162
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,839
Please don't take it to heart.

163
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:05,399
No,

164
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,439
Am I wrong?

165
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,920
He's just Lord Ning's bastard
from Ning Manor.

166
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,920
Don't talk nonsense!

167
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,879
I'll say it anyway!

168
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:12,279
Even Ning Manor doesn't want him.

169
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,680
What future could he possibly have?

170
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:15,160
Just look at him.

171
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:16,920
He can't do any heavy lifting.

172
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:18,000
If I let him stay here,

173
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:19,920
I'd have to wait on him hand and foot!

174
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:20,639
Shut up!

175
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:21,680
Brother!

176
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:22,399
Brother Mei! Mother!

177
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,160
What are you doing, mother?

178
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:26,000
Mei Jiu, how dare you hit me!

179
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:27,160
Get back inside the room!

180
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:27,959
I won't!

181
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:28,959
I'm staying right here.

182
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,639
Since when do you run this house?

183
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:31,480
Get back inside!

184
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:34,759
Sister-in-law.

185
00:08:38,399 --> 00:08:38,960
Brother Mei.

186
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,279
I'm sorry.

187
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,440
This is all my fault.

188
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,080
I've caused you trouble.

189
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,080
Master Ning, you overstate it.

190
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:47,039
Having you stay in our home

191
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,480
is an honor for my sister and me.

192
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:50,879
Rest assured,

193
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,200
I can't promise lavish meals,

194
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,320
but you'll have full meals every day.

195
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:59,559
Then I'll be imposing on you for a while.

196
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,679
No need to treat me differently.

197
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,440
I'll eat whatever you eat.

198
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:04,799
Sis.

199
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:05,840
Um,

200
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,200
go tidy up the side room.

201
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,879
I need to find a way

202
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,679
to earn silver and repay
Xiao Mei's family.

203
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:14,200
That's right.

204
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,799
Top Scholar Pavilion.

